name: Making a Case Against Kevin Then Voting

steps.name: Given the user is on the Elucidat learning platform
Then the title is "Finding the Truth"
Then the user clicks on START button
Then the user clicks on Making a case against Kevin
Then I click on JUDGE THIS button
Then I click on Guilty Radio
Then I click on Vote button
Then I verify NOT GUILTY! element
Then I click on the continue button_1
Then I click on the continue button_2
Then I click on continue button 2
Then I verify YOU DECIDE element
Then I click on continue button 3
Then I click on flip button
Then I click on can be reliable radio
Then I click on Vote button again
Then I verify Our expert agrees element
Then I click on the continue button_1

fullName: Voting Then Decision Making on Elucidat Learning Platform: Making a Case Against Kevin Then Voting
